    "These tasks include, but are not limited to, pattern recognition, computer vision, and natural language processing [12].",
    "The dynamic and expansive nature of AI means that its definition is fluid, often evolving alongside advancements in the field.",
    "This phenomenon, sometimes referred to as the \"AI effect\", highlights the shifting boundary of what is considered AI [13].",
    "Innovations once deemed revolutionary become standard over time, thus no longer classified under AI, while emerging, more sophisticated technologies are labelled as AI.As we venture deeper into the specifics, AI's application in specialised fields, including the legal sector, represents its more advanced and complex forms.",
